::: Set made it to the Predacon base. Though, he could see several bots 
outside scuffeling. He thought for a moment if being on this planet for a 
prolonged period of time made the bots into savages....:::

::: he had no time for this. He had to get in and out. He picked up his 
communicator :::

::: Set ::: Predacons...this is Set. Im holding your Commander prisoner. If 
you dont let me inside right now, I will have him killed.

::: There was a short pause, and Black Aracnia shot back ::: Good, kill him. 
I think hes the bigg-

::: Another voice broke in, scolding Black Aracnia ::: Sorry about that. You 
can enter, with no wepons.

::: set ::: Very well. Just have the tech box waiting for me.

::: Suddenly, with a creak, a small side door opened and Set entered to see 
two beautiful females there, fully armed. The spider gave him a dirty look 
and gabbed him in the ribs. The Pheniox smiles, and then dug her talons into 
his shoulders, leading him down the hall. :::

::: Black Aracnia picked up the tech box off of a table and handed it to him 
::: So, now can we have our rightious leader back?

::: Set ::: Possible....you do know your both raveshing, dont you?

::: Black Aracnia ::: shut up and get out. 

::: Within moments, Set found himself on the Predacons door step, and 
auto-guns firing at him :::
